sa:

  → development/databases/SQL-Server/administration/schemas/sys/objects/views/sysprocesses[`sys.sysprocesses`]

  Each connection (record in `dm_exec_connections`) is associated with *one* session (record in → development/databases/SQL-Server/administration/schemas/sys/objects/views/dm/exec/sessions[`sys.dm_exec_sessions`]) but
  not every session is associated with a connection.

